Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hewan Suci?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hofvalpnir adalah dewa pelindung\Nyang dahulu kala telah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menyelamatkan nenek moyang kami\Ndari setan danau yang menguasai tanah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itulah, bunga ini dikatakan sebagai\Nbunga ajaib yang tumbuh dari air mata dewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bunga seberharga itu,\Napa benar kami boleh memintanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dirimu adalah penyelamat desa,\Nambil saja sebanyak yang kamu mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:01:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggal kembali ke Belkaim\Ndan membuat obatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu bikin macam-macam dari Beri Lidaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Kades!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Desanya! Desanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya Tuhan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bee, ayo padamkan apinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Byui!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Clay, tolong selamatkan warga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untungnya tidak ada yang luka parah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi desanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Engache tiba-tiba datang tengah malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia meminta bunga Iver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kubilang kami sudah tahu bahwa itu racun\Ndan tidak akan menyerahkannya lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menyulut api?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Gonza tidak ketemu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gonza itu, anak yang paling pertama\Ndekat padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gonza!\NGonza tidak kelihatan di mana pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melihatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melihat Gonza dibawa pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kami kelabakan\Nkarena Pak Engache menyulut api,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia menggotong Gonza\Ndan pergi ke arah danau.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang mau jadi penculik, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa diampuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Search!\NBentangkan dengan kekuatan penuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka bergerombol hampir seratus orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan masalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tu-Tunggu dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu berbahaya, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ditemani petualang Rank A\Nyang kuatnya bukan main.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami pasti menyelamatkan Gonza,\Njadi tunggu saja dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka sedang berpesta, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya berpesta setelah membakar\Ndesa yang tidak berdosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darah di sekujur tubuhku jadi mendidih!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham kamu marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Gonza bisa terancam\Nkalau kita ketahuan menyerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wujudmu begitu tapi langsung menurut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus bagaimana aku\Nmelampiaskan amarah ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekuatan yang meluap ini\Ningin segera kulepaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Woi, Raja Iblis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar pergerakan kita tidak ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menghilangkan wujud, kamuflase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, hapus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat sekali terbakarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu yang cocok buat minum miras.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, apa—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir Fosch-nya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm, sepertinya kita\Nmemang jadi tidak terlihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya mereka berkumpul di lantai atas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ayo terus maju.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takeru, kenapa barusan kamu\Nmengumpulkan barang-barang itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya kita tidak tahu di mana racun\Ndan bukti kejahatan mereka disembunyikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar pria tanpa celah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal sudah kita periksa semuanya,\NGonza tetap tidak ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, minta saja untuk diantar\Noleh yang menyembunyikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat muka setengah mati mereka, tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu akibatnya kalau menentang Pak Engache!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, tetap saja lokasi bunganya\Ntidak dibocorkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah gunanya si bocah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita paksa dia atau\Njadikan peringatan untuk mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agenda menggoreng harga\Nracun Iver sudah mau selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sampai gagal, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kenapa harganya\Nbisa tergoreng begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Istri kepala keluarga Lusellavach\Nyang terkemuka itu sudah dibuat sakit parah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyakit yang para ahli penyembuh\Nterbaik sekalipun tidak tahu obatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tersebar rumor\Nbahwa itu disebabkan racun Iver,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti bakal banyak orang\Nyang antre ingin memakainya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini rencana rahasia, tutup rapat mulutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau kutenggelamkan di danau Galeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takeru, aku sudah tidak tahan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Byu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, mengamuklah sebuas yang kalian mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jangan sampai membunuh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dimengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ada apa?\N- Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersiaplah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku tidak sudi mati di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bawakan itu kemari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi masih belum bisa dikendalikan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat bawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial, sial!\NKenapa jadi begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Engas, ayo pindahkan anak itu,\Ndi mana dia sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kan, dia di bangunan terpisah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat bawakan itu dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Barusan itu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata ada bangunan terpisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuserahkan padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ampas banget malah cuma aku\Nyang harus jaga bocil di saat begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oi, oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bee, kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gonza, apa kamu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau iya, jawab aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gonza!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kamu baik-baik saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mundurlah sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pasti takut, Gonza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo pulang ke desa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kabur!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, itu bukan ulah Clay, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi di dalam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu setan danau!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setan danau?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Clay di wujud raja iblis, sih,\Ntidak perlu dikhawatirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tergantung kecocokannya,\Nmungkin perlu kubantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gonza, karena bahaya, bisa sembunyi di—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia habis diculik dan disekap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti gelisah kalau harus sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gonza, bisa pegangan\Nyang erat ke punggungku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gonza, jangan sampai lepas, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kupuji keberanianmu\Nuntuk berdiri di hadapanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anemon laut?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dark Anemone, Rank B?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemanggilnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu ngapain, sih, Engas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon!\NTolong aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini salahmu sendiri, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kutanya detailnya nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Clay, maaf lama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kamu berhasil menyelamatkannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, tentakel menjengkelkan!\NKupotong berkali-kali pun tidak ada habisnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu sekalian saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentangkan Ice Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, sekarang jadi lamban!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi masih belum mati!\NOtaknya harus dihancurkan dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bulatan yang di tengah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong urus Gonza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Byui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punya kemampuan unik sebanyak apa pun,\Ntetap gawat kalau tenggelam dalam racun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, aku malah mempertaruhkan nyawa\Ndemi menyelamatkan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata istilah bertindak\Nsebelum berpikir itu betulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kamu mengoceh ini itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tetap saja tidak bisa mengabaikan\Norang di hadapanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat itu, dunia ini\Nmengarah ke jalur yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski sebagai gantinya,\Nmuncul anomali di sana-sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kuberi hadiah untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya aku juga mencintai dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi akan kukabulkan keinginanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kesal juga kalau harus mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal masih banyak yang ingin kulakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang telah memanggilku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengin makan enak lebih banyak lagi,\Npadahal aku baru saja dapat syoyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wahai engkau penerima berkah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau melihat pertumbuhan Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekuatanku telah bangkit kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Clay dan Brolite, yah, tanpa aku pun\Nmereka pasti baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Engkau penerima berkah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, guntingku!\NGunting sakti mandragunaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengarkan... omonganku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mati seenak udelmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha-Halo, namaku Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Hofvalpnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayak pernah dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, apakah ini rumahnya Hof—\Napakah ini rumahmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau iya, mohon maaf\Nsudah seenaknya tenggelam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihatlah ke bawah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal tadinya hitam pekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu telah memurnikan tanahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulunya, aku kehilangan kekuatan akibat\Ndigerogoti Esensi Magis yang terkumpul di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk menjaga tanah subur dan air yang bersih,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:16:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku menciptakan bunga Iver\Nyang memiliki kekuatan penyucian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski aku jadi batu karena kehabisan tenaga,\Ntanah ini seharusnya sudah terlindungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hingga dinodai oleh tangan\Nanak manusia yang jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si Engas, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi berkatmu yang menyerap\NElemen Magis itu, kekuatanku kembali
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan danaunya murni kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kalau aku bisa berguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kamu baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku diselamatkan dewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga telah kamu selamatkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti impas, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takeru, kamu bicara sama siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan suara dewa ini\Nhanya bisa didengar olehku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takeru, kuucapkan\Nterima kasih tak terhingga untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gonza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu yakin ini betulan aman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu saja yang khawatir berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, mendekatlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sihir yang terpikirkan saat di Vozlao,\Npasti bakal berguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, ini idemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti sudah dipikirkan dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatiku sudah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, akan kumulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat Gate, sihir untuk berteleportasi,\Nperjalanan pulang kami hanya sekejap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dibantu ahli obat\Nkepercayaan serikat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuat obat dari bunganya\Ntidak memakan waktu lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan diminum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takeru, tolong periksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah aman, racunnya berhasil dinetralkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibunda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Engache telah melibatkan kami\Nke sesuatu yang tidak terduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, si Engas sudah kuserahkan pada Tuan Tanah\Nbeserta barang bukti yang banyak,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi desa ini sudah aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tidak tahu harus bagaimana\Nmembalas budi padamu, Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu dibalas,\Ntapi kalau boleh sebagai gantinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan dimakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enaknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namanya kentang mentega syoyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kentang mentega syoyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Kades, ini sekadar usulan dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa jual Beri Lidaz\Ndalam jumlah besar padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bi-Bisa, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, tolong perluas kebun Lidaz\Ndengan hasil penjualan tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau sebanyak itu, nanti kamu sendiri\Ntidak bisa menghabiskannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ini bisa tenar di Belkaim,\NBeri Lidaz bisa jadi produk khas Desa Ashus, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Su-Sumpah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana rasanya setelah\Nmenyelesaikan tugas besar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja melelahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa rasanya aku berhalusinasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halusinasi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, langitnya bersinar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halusinasimu itu...\NSepertinya aku juga bisa melihatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan halusinasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kalau tidak salah, kamu...\NHof-apalah-pnir, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa bisa di Belkaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah terlalu lama berdiam di satu tempat,\Nwahai engkau penerima berkah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takeru, aku memutuskan\Nuntuk ikut dengan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku telah tinggal di tanah itu\Nuntuk waktu yang lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa bantuanku sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi aku ingin pergi ke daerah lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dewi Hofvalpnir, kenapa kamu\Ningin mengikuti pria di luar nalar ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ikut dengan Takeru,\Nkupikir dunia akan jadi menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, kamu menginginkan kuda, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang menginginkan kuda, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, tidak ada kuda\Nyang lebih hebat dari diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuizinkan kamu menaiki punggungku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi hari ini kamu mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita pergi ke mana saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang menginginkan seekor kuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kok dewa malah jadi temanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah sangat siap, Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ayo, sekarang mau ke mana?\N- Bagaimana, ya, ini pasti...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pasti...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakal jadi masalah nantinya!
